  "prompt": "When did Travelzoo launch its IPO?",
  "response": "Travelzoo launched its initial public offering (IPO) on **June 16, 2023**. The company went public by completing a merger with RiverVest Global, Inc. II, a special purpose acquisition company (SPAC). Following the merger, Travelzoo began trading on the NASDAQ stock exchange under the ticker symbol **TZOO**.\n\n**Key Details:**\n- **IPO Date:** June 16, 2023\n- **Ticker Symbol:** TZOO\n- **Exchange:** NASDAQ\n\nThis move marked Travelzoo's transition from a privately held company to a publicly traded entity, allowing it to raise capital from public investors to support its growth and expansion initiatives.",
